      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">The Speed Verdict</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Mixo wins for landing pages.</strong> 47 seconds to published, $9/month. Done and moving on.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Framer wins for portfolios.</strong> Takes 3+ hours but looks stunning. Code export included.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>The brutal math:</strong> Is an extra 2 hours worth a 0.1% conversion improvement? For MVPs, no. For design businesses, yes.
      </p>
